OL,3,CChannel Islands Coop dividend to be
OL,4,Cvoted on this week as profits rise
OL,6,FThe Channel Islands Coop made more
OL,7,Fsales and higher returns over the last
OL,8,Ftrading year.
OL,10,FIts turnover surpassed #220 million
OL,11,Ffor the 52 weeks to Sunday 11 January,
OL,12,Fa 4% increase, while profit rose by
OL,13,Falmost 7% to #7.2 million.
OL,15,FNet surplus, the amount left over
OL,16,Fafter all expenses and taxes have been
OL,17,Fpaid, grew to #1 million.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
