OL,3,CChannel Islands Coop dividend to be
OL,4,Cvoted on this week as profits rise
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the organisation says more
OL,7,Fthan #10 million was returned to its
OL,8,Fmembers through savings, dividends and
OL,9,Finterest.
OL,11,FThe CI Coop will hold two public
OL,12,Fmeetings this week, where members will
OL,13,Fbe asked to vote on whether to accept
OL,14,Fa 2% dividend.
OL,16,FThe Guernsey Annual Members Meeting
OL,17,Fwill take place on Tuesday 19 May at
OL,18,FSt Pierre Park Hotel, while the Jersey
OL,19,Fone will be hosted at Radisson Blu
OL,20,FHotel on Wednesday 20 May.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/4
