OL,3,CChannel Islands Coop dividend to be
OL,4,Cvoted on this week as profits rise
OL,6,FThe organisation's Chief Executive
OL,7,FOfficer, Mark Cox, says: "While cost
OL,8,Fof living pressures remain a challenge
OL,9,Facross both the islands, the Society
OL,10,Fhas taken deliberate action to support
OL,11,Fmembers through everyday pricing and
OL,12,Ftargeted savings.
OL,14,F"We have strengthened our performance,
OL,15,Finvested in pricing, and ensured that
OL,16,Fmore money goes back into members'
OL,17,Fpockets every time they shop with us."
OL,19,FThere are now around 128,000 CI Coop
OL,20,Fmembers, accounting for more than
OL,21,Feight out of ten transactions.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/4
